## Base Repository Methods

Tất cả các repository đều kế thừa từ [BaseRepository](file:///d:/code/SW391/be-swp391-eye-wear/src/repositories/base.repository.ts#18-159) với các methods sau:

### [findById(id: string)](file:///d:/code/SW391/be-swp391-eye-wear/src/repositories/base.repository.ts#57-63)
Tìm document theo ID

### [findOne(filter: FilterQuery)](file:///d:/code/SW391/be-swp391-eye-wear/src/repositories/base.repository.ts#64-73)
Tìm 1 document theo điều kiện (chỉ trả về documents chưa bị xóa)

### [find(filter: Partial<T>, options?: PaginationOptions)](file:///d:/code/SW391/be-swp391-eye-wear/src/repositories/base.repository.ts#74-84)
Tìm nhiều documents với pagination

**PaginationOptions:**
```typescript
{
  page?: number,      // Default: 1
  limit?: number,     // Default: 10
  sortBy?: string,    // Default: 'createdAt'
  sortOrder?: 'asc' | 'desc'  // Default: 'desc'
}
```

**Returns:**
```typescript
{
  data: T[],
  total: number,
  page: number,
  limit: number,
  totalPages: number
}
```

### [findAll(options?: PaginationOptions)](file:///d:/code/SW391/be-swp391-eye-wear/src/repositories/base.repository.ts#85-93)
Lấy tất cả documents với pagination

### [create(data: Partial<T>)](file:///d:/code/SW391/be-swp391-eye-wear/src/repositories/base.repository.ts#94-100)
Tạo document mới

### [update(id: string, data: Partial<T>)](file:///d:/code/SW391/be-swp391-eye-wear/src/repositories/base.repository.ts#101-110)
Cập nhật document theo ID

### [updateByFilter(filter: FilterQuery, data: UpdateQuery)](file:///d:/code/SW391/be-swp391-eye-wear/src/repositories/base.repository.ts#110-119)
Cập nhật document theo điều kiện

### [delete(id: string)](file:///d:/code/SW391/be-swp391-eye-wear/src/repositories/base.repository.ts#120-130)
Soft delete (set deletedAt = current date)

### [hardDelete(id: string)](file:///d:/code/SW391/be-swp391-eye-wear/src/repositories/base.repository.ts#131-137)
Xóa vĩnh viễn khỏi database

### [count(filter?: FilterQuery)](file:///d:/code/SW391/be-swp391-eye-wear/src/repositories/base.repository.ts#138-147)
Đếm số lượng documents (chỉ đếm documents chưa bị xóa)

### [exists(filter: FilterQuery)](file:///d:/code/SW391/be-swp391-eye-wear/src/repositories/base.repository.ts#148-158)
Kiểm tra document có tồn tại không

---

## Usage Examples

### Creating an Order
```typescript
const newOrder = await orderRepository.create({
  type: OrderType.NORMAL,
  status: OrderStatus.PENDING,
  products: [
    {
      product: { product_id: 'frame123', sku: 'FR-001', price: 500000 },
      quantity: 1,
      lens: {
        lens_id: 'lens456',
        sku: 'LN-001',
        parameters: {
          left: { SPH: -2.5, CYL: -0.5, AXIS: 90 },
          right: { SPH: -2.0, CYL: -0.75, AXIS: 85 },
          PD: 63
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  price: 800000,
  isVerified: { status: VerifyOrderStatus.PENDING },
  assignment: { status: AssignmentOrderStatus.PENDING }
});
```

### Creating an Invoice
```typescript
const newInvoice = await invoiceRepository.create({
  orders: ['order123', 'order456'],
  owner: 'customer789',
  totalPrice: 1500000,
  totalDiscount: 100000,
  voucher: ['voucher001'],
  address: {
    street: '123 Nguyen Hue',
    ward: 'Ben Nghe',
    city: 'Ho Chi Minh'
  },
  status: InvoiceStatus.PENDING,
  fullName: 'Nguyen Van A',
  phone: '0901234567'
});
```

### Updating Order Status
```typescript
await orderRepository.update('order123', {
  status: OrderStatus.APPROVED
});
```

### Assigning Manager to Invoice
```typescript
await invoiceRepository.update('invoice123', {
  status: InvoiceStatus.ONBOARD,
  manager_onboard: 'manager456'
});
```

### Finding Orders with Pagination
```typescript
const result = await orderRepository.find(
  { type: OrderType.MANUFACTURING },
  { page: 1, limit: 20, sortBy: 'createdAt', sortOrder: 'desc' }
);
// result.data - array of orders
// result.total - total count
// result.totalPages - total pages
```
